title: How We Knew Our Partners Were “Made For Us” + Listener Accidentally Bought A Tesla Online + Battle Of The Bands: 90’s Country Edition!
itunes:title: How We Knew Our Partners Were “Made For Us” + Listener Accidentally Bought A Tesla Online + Battle Of The Bands: 90’s Country Edition!
description:
Bobby talked about hearing “Made For You” by Jake Owen on the radio yesterday and wanted to know the moments we all knew our partners were “meant for us”. A caller has their own Bonehead Story of the Day: She accidentally bought a Tesla on her phone using Apple Pay. We play a famous fiddle from a country song…Bobby and the rest of the show have to name the song. We put Alan Jackson versus George Strait against each other in the Battle of the Bands: 90’s Country Edition.
